(143, 0, 'OCS 2750', 'Editorial', 'Sprint 29', 'PAM emancipation', 'Bring the OCS Events ID logic that connects WON to Forge to other entities. At the moment, the only entitiy in which we are able to create a connection between WON and Forge is the OCS Evente.\n\nWe do so through the Entity ID or the Event ID (BTW: you never specified which one is really the active one?).\nWe would like a similar logic applied to other entities:\nAthletes\nDisciplines\nSports\nCountries\nNOCs<br/>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n2750, 2751, 2752, 2753, 2754', '<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://deltatre.atlassian.net/browse/OCS-2750\">OCS 2750</a>', 'next sprint', 'true', 9, '#e2dd3b', '', 'false', ''),
