(156, 0, 'OCS 2671', 'SEO', 'Sprint 27', 'Investigation: allow Google rendering properly OCS pages', 'An investigation is done so that we identify the best way for allowing Google to rendering properly OCS pages.\nMain issue is that Google is not rendering content loaded through React (and, more in general, JS).\nThe outcome of this spike must be: the list of activities needed for the implementation of the solution\nrelevant costs in terms of story points', '<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://deltatre.atlassian.net/browse/OCS-2671\">OCS 2671</a>', 'in progress 12/10', 'false', 5, '#63dea6', 'SEO', 'false', '1'),
(157, 0, 'OCS 2454', 'TechOps', 'Sprint 27 ', 'NEW OCS Public IP RANGE for Whitelisting', 'We have defined a new Public Ip Range for our corporate network:\nOBS IT: 185.248.205.0/24\nOCS BIT: 185.248.204.0/24\nWe would need to add this Ip Ranges to the existing whitelist in order to grant access to all the relevant systems at Delta3 that are now protected with a firewall (Forge, FTP Servers and any other system that is protected by whitelist).', '<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://deltatre.atlassian.net/browse/OCS-2454\">OCS 2454</a>', 'completed 12/10', 'true', 6, '#a1cfea', 'backend', 'false', '1'),
(158, 0, 'OCS 2719', 'TechOPs', 'Sprint 27', 'Detailed up-to-date list of DNS records', 'we need you provide us a full and up-to-date list of all public DNS records associated with all Forge servers running on our Alibaba account including development, staging and production.\n\nFrom your documentation, there are records that are not in DNS and it should be there like these ones showing Non-existent Domain (NXDOMAIN)\n\nprd-ocs-common-lb-rabbitmq.prd.ocs.deltatre.net\nstg-ocs-common-lb-rabbitmq.stg.ocs.deltatre.net\n\nThere are other DNS records that are simple not documented or not exist like EPG Importer server for Staging:  stg-ocs-common-seq-01', '<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://deltatre.atlassian.net/browse/OCS-2719\">OCS 2719</a>', 'Completed 12/10', 'true', 7, '#a1cfea', 'backend', 'false', '0.5'),
(159, 0, 'OCS 2755', 'Editorial', 'Sprint 27', 'Assessment: Add stories in \"All video\" pages', 'The \"All video\" page of the single sport, athlete and event should show not only VODs, but also stories (same tagging rules of VODs).\nBased on this request, deltatre will provide OCS with the feasibility (and relevant estimate) of some solutions in order to develop this. E.g. limit the number of items displayed create a new \"Stories\" tab and show All video and All stories tabs only if they contain content etc.', '<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://deltatre.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/OC/pages/229572620/Add+Stories+to+different+modules+and+sections\">Confluence</a>', 'in progress 12/10', 'false', 5, '#63dea6', 'UX', 'false', '1'),
(160, 0, 'OCS 2184', 'TechOps', 'Sprint 29', 'Lazyload on images', 'Images lazy loading is implemented on the web site, so that page loading time is reduced.\nThe following solution is implemented: images are loaded in their worst quality as soon as the page is loading then the right image format is loaded', '<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://deltatre.atlassian.net/browse/OCS-2184\">OCS 2184</a>', 'Warranty issue', 'true', 9, 'magenta', 'Performance', 'false', '5'),
(163, 0, 'OCS 2732, 33, 34, 35, 36, 37', 'Editorial', 'Sprint 29', 'Add Stories in multiple modules and sections', 'Preserving the latest and tag-related business rules as they are, we want all Mosaics to be populated by default behavior and to be ready to host Stories (both News and Features).', '<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://deltatre.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/OC/pages/229572620/Add+Stories+to+different+modules+and+sections\">Confluence Page</a>', 'next sprint', 'true', 9, '#e2dd3b', 'UX', 'false', '9'),
