(177, 0, 'OCS 2751', 'TechOps', '', 'PAM emancipation: VOD/EPG ingestion: automatic tagging of non-PAM athletes', 'Done if: A new field is added for athletes in Forge, where editors can manually write an athlete ID (field name TBD). EPG and VOD importers are updated so that, if VODs and EPGs coming from WON / MPX contain the same athlete ID(s) (field name TBD), the EPG / VOD is automatically tagged by that athlete(s) in Forge.', '<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://deltatre.atlassian.net/browse/OCS-2751\">OCS 2751</a>', 'in queue', 'true', 75, '#ffffff', 'workflow', 'false', '5'),
