(182, 0, 'OCS 2722', 'Editorial', '', 'Import 6 new discipline from PAM', 'The IOC has added to the PAM the following disciplines that will be used extensively during BAYOG:\n\n3x3 Basketball\nKarate\nBreaking\nBeach Handball\nFutsal\nRoller Speed Skating\n\nCan you please connect temporarily to the PAM so when users send a VOD or EPG the import is done automatically and no manual tagging is required from Iacopo Radaelli&#39;s team.', '<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://deltatre.atlassian.net/browse/OCS-2722\">OCS 2722</a>', 'in queue', 'true', 80, '#ffffff', 'UX', 'false', ''),
